      "text": "<b>Therefore</b>, you should use a language that suits the participants, being expressive and fascinating at the same time. Your voice should resemble the suspense that should prevail in the participants. You should speak loud enough that in can be heard in the whole room. If you run a lot of seminars and you experience problems with your voice you should consider training you voice, control your breathing and ensure proper posture.\n  ",
      "id": "1cfbf7d550071274",
