      "text": "Use short, simple sentences. Technical termini should only be used if they are well known. Use a verbal style. Speak slowly and insert breaks to give the listeners a chance to process complicated facts. Accentuate important topics by changing your voice, by varying your talking rate or by repeating them. Speak loud enough and do not use too much dialect.\n  ",
